        "when": "2025-06",
        "text": "We made the perfect choice when we chose Candid Studios for our wedding.  There was a professional photographer and professional videographers on their squad, and they were amazing.  We wanted Colorado wedding photographers who could show off the natural beauty of our mountain setting and the emotional moments we shared.  Candid Studios did a great job on all fronts.\n\nThey got there early, were very organized, and took hundreds of beautiful pictures.  The wedding film in Colorado Springs was very emotional. It had a cinematic edit that included drone footage, vows, and speeches.  The wedding videographers in Colorado Springs definitely went above and beyond.\n\nWe also liked that they have an affordable engagement photographer that made our first session together so pleasant and comfortable.  We were able to trust them more before the wedding day.  Candid Studios is the place to go if you want cheap wedding photographers who act like high-end professionals.  They are all you want and then some."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-08",
        "text": "Candid Studios separated out from the other wedding photographers in Colorado Springs because of their flair and professionalism. On the day of our wedding, their photographer fit right in and took pictures of everything without getting in the way. We also hired them to shoot the wedding video, which was really emotional and like a movie. The pictures and videos showed off our personalities and love story flawlessly. This is the crew to trust if you want wedding photos and videos from Colorado Springs that seem real, timeless, and gorgeous."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-06",
        "text": "From the day we got engaged until the day we got married, Candid Studios was there for us. Their Colorado Springs engagement photographer set the mood with a fun and romantic photo shoot. Then, their team of Colorado wedding photographers took wonderful pictures and videos of our wedding day. Working with them is a dream."
      },
      {
